## Example Projects

- [Todoist](https://todoist.com/): Todoist is a popular task management application with features similar to those described above.
- [Trello](https://trello.com/): Trello is a visual project management tool that allows users to create and manage tasks on a digital board.
- [Asana](https://asana.com/): Asana is a team collaboration tool that includes task management features for both individuals and teams.
